              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Software update i security patching</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Tehnička podrška (email/WhatsApp)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Monitoring uptime-a i performansi</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Kome je namijenjeno</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Svima kojima treba dugoročna stabilnost i podrška bez IT tima.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Cijena</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Od 30–60 KM mjesečno (zavisno od obima)</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600"><strong>Napomena:</strong> Uključene male izmjene sadržaja, ali ne i nove feature development.</p>
            </div>
